<p>The Godwin Repository is completely dependent on <strong>you</strong>. The continued operation of the site relies on the participation of its users submitting, commenting on, and updating entries. Luckily, finding content on the site is extremely simple. To locate a record, simply use the search bar at the top of every page to input any relevant keywords. Alternatively, you can check out the most recent and most popular entries, which are displayed on our homepage.</p>

<p>Can't find what you're looking for? If the record you want doesn't exist in our database, then you have two easy options to submit it yourself and join the ranks of our dedicated content creators. If you happen to have our site open in front of you, just head over to our <a href="#">submit an entry</a> page and give us a little information about your link and your entry is all set.</p>

